lemons

various scripts

brightness.lisp:
  - adjust screen brightness

mpd-next.lisp:
  - move to next/previous song while remaining paused
  - ipod style "jump to start of song" behavior when moving to previous song
  - toggle play/pause

switch-desktop.lisp
  - cycle through desktops with feh

citrus.lisp
  - tmux status bar
  - writes to a file ~/.citrus

touchoff.scm
  - turn wacom pen and touch tablet touch capabilities off
